-- Assuming that everybody in our database has a bill coming due, and that 
-- all of them will pay on time, write a query to compute the total gross 
-- income we expect to receive.

-- Answer:

--   gross
--  --------
--  678.50
-- (1 row)

-- Solution:

SELECT sum(services.price) AS gross
FROM services
JOIN customers_services
ON services.id = customers_services.service_id;